OBJECTIVE: To investigate longevity in women after bilateral 
salpingo-oophorectomy (BSOE), not given hormonal replacement therapy (HRT) 
post-operatively, as compared to the national mean.
STUDY DESIGN: Long-term follow-up study of a historical cohort of young women 
